Pseudokod
-------
**GameControllers Metod play för en omgång av 21:**

    Call player_play method when play-button is clicked.

    player_play()
        Player hand append card
        INCREMENT value
        IF sum value is 21:
            PRINT player wins
            EXIT
        IF sum value is over 21:
            PRINT player looses
            EXIT

    IF STOP button clicked:
        Call bank_play method

    bank_play()
        Bank hand append card
        INCREMENT value
        IF sum value is 21:
            PRINT bank wins
            EXIT
        IF sum value is over 21:
            PRINT player wins
            EXIT
        IF sum value is equal or better than player:
            PRINT Bank wins
            EXIT
        IF sum value is less than player:
            PRINT player wins
            EXIT
